  combo: 43
  dialogue:
  - "hehe\u2026 whiskers certainly knows how to grab everyone\u2019s attention. Hehe,
    I can go right up there and dye them purple!"
  - "What an entertainment that\u2019d be! But I am the Court jester, not he! "
  - "Worry not, worry not, little flower! No one out-jesters the Jester Queen! Hm,
    maybe except for dyed whiskers\u2026"
  - 'Those whiskers may be odd as they are, I fear he will complain about it for
    weeks to come if you do. '
  - aw...
